parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the automatic sliding doors can cause the doors to open or close unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when children are in the vehicle.
symptoms: The doors open or close erratically
the doors open while driving
the doors fail to close
the doors open when the vehicle is locked
the alarm sounds when the doors are closed
the doors come open on bumps
and the doors malfunction repeatedly despite repairs.

the vehicle has a wobbly ride
the rear tires cup and become out of balance
the vehicle is difficult to stop and handle.
